      <h1>Data Deletion</h1>

      <br>

      <p>
        Cuukin Cooking School Ltd. respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data, including the rights to have your data forgotten.
      </p>

      <p>
        Please refer back to our <%= link_to "Terms & Conditions", privacy_path, target: "_blank" %> if you have any doubts on how we manage your data.
